DE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udoaal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>doaal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/17/02 1:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just a spell thought</span><hr size=1> Those are for dr00ds lol.  It would be nice to have a single target snare for quadding but I doubt VI will ever give it to us. <p><FONT COLOR="990000"><H4><B>
